reviewtext: This is awesome, especially for the cost.  Just plug and play.  I have 5 port modem/switch from Verizon for my internet and needed more lines hooked up in my house then just the 5.  So took this, plugged into the modem/switch and bang, 4 more ports, nothing else to do.  If you need to expand your wired device this is a great addition.  Just plug it in and your all set to go.
